original: Bjarne, Nils Johan Otto, läroverksadjunkt, Laholm, f. 5/8/85 i Tryde, Krist. 1. G. 19 m. ämneslär. Gulli Bergqvist. Barn: se denna. — Folkskoll :ex. 07, stud:ex. i Hälsingb. 11, fil. kand. i Lund 13, fil. mag. 14. E. lär. i Nederkalix 15, ord. ämneslär. där 15, rektor o. ord. ämneslär. v. komm. mellansk. i Laholm 15-30, rektor o. adj. v. samrealsk. där 30-33, lä-roverksadj. sed. 33. Hobby: vinodling.
translated: Bjarne, Nils Johan Otto, high school teacher, from Laholm, born August 5, 1885 in Tryde, Krist. Married in 1919 to subject teacher Gulli Bergqvist. Children: see this. - Graduated from elementary school in 1907, studied at Hälsingb. in 1911, received Bachelor of Arts degree from Lund in 1913, and Master of Arts in 1914. Became a teacher in Nederkalix in 1915, became a regular subject teacher there in 1915, principal and regular subject teacher in the central municipality of Laholm from 1915-1930, principal and adjunct at the secondary school there from 1930-1933, and high school teacher since 1933. Hobby: vineyard cultivation.

occupation.name: Principal and Adjunct at the Secondary School
